  "summary": "Main\nThe Baltic headline FBX index has remained mostly unchanged over the past week, at 2,137 compared to 2,135. Some backhaul routes saw quite significant increases week-on-week given the ongoing tariff scenario. FBX02 : +25% ($356 → $445)\nFBX04 : +10% ($369 → $408)\nOther indices ( FBX01, FBX03, FBX11, FBX13 ) were slightly negative to flat.",
